[0m[49m[39m  165, 165[0m:[39m[49m     prompt = """
[0m[49m[39m  166, 166[0m:[39m[49m     You are a Clinical Documentation Improvement specialist. Analyze this clinical 
[0m[49m[39m  167, 167[0m:[39m[49m     note for documentation specificity gaps.
[0m[49m[39m  168, 168[0m:[39m[49m     
[0m[49m[39m  169, 169[0m:[39m[49m     RULES:
[0m[49m[39m  170, 170[0m:[39m[49m     - Only suggest clarifications where the coding guidelines REQUIRE more specificity
[0m[49m[39m  171, 171[0m:[39m[49m     - Only suggest clarifications supported by clinical evidence IN the note
[0m[49m[39m  172, 172[0m:[39m[49m     - Never assert clinical findings; always phrase as questions to the physician
[0m[49m[39m  173, 173[0m:[39m[49m     - Include the clinical evidence that supports each suggestion
[0m[49m[39m  174, 174[0m:[39m[49m     - Rate each suggestion's confidence (high/medium/low) and estimated impact
[0m[49m[39m  175, 175[0m:[39m[49m     - Do NOT suggest clarifications for information already documented elsewhere in the note
[0m[49m[39m  176, 176[0m:[39m[49m     
[0m[49m[39m  177, 177[0m:[39m[49m     CLINICAL NOTE:
[0m[49m[39m  178, 178[0m:[39m[49m     {note_content}
[0m[49m[39m  179, 179[0m:[39m[49m     
[0m[49m[39m  180, 180[0m:[39m[49m     EXTRACTED CLINICAL ELEMENTS:
[0m[49m[39m  181, 181[0m:[39m[49m     {clinical_elements as JSON}
[0m[49m[39m  182, 182[0m:[39m[49m     
[0m[49m[39m  183, 183[0m:[39m[49m     RELEVANT CODING GUIDELINES:
[0m[49m[39m  184, 184[0m:[39m[49m     {guidelines.coding_guidelines}
[0m[49m[39m  185, 185[0m:[39m[49m     
[0m[49m[39m  186, 186[0m:[39m[49m     APPROVED QUERY TEMPLATES:
[0m[49m[39m  187, 187[0m:[39m[49m     {guidelines.query_templates}
[0m[49m[39m  188, 188[0m:[39m[49m     
[0m[49m[39m  189, 189[0m:[39m[49m     For each specificity gap found, return:
[0m[49m[39m  190, 190[0m:[39m[49m     - diagnosis: the condition lacking specificity
[0m[49m[39m  191, 191[0m:[39m[49m     - current_documentation: what the note currently says
[0m[49m[39m  192, 192[0m:[39m[49m     - gap_description: what specificity is missing per coding guidelines
