[0m[49m[39m  194, 194[0m:[39m[49m     - suggested_query: physician-friendly question requesting clarification
[0m[49m[39m  195, 195[0m:[39m[49m     - confidence: high/medium/low (how confident are you this is a real gap?)
[0m[49m[39m  196, 196[0m:[39m[49m     - estimated_impact: high/medium/low (DRG/reimbursement significance)
[0m[49m[39m  197, 197[0m:[39m[49m     - icd10_current: likely current code assignment
[0m[49m[39m  198, 198[0m:[39m[49m     - icd10_potential: likely code if documentation is clarified
[0m[49m[39m  199, 199[0m:[39m[49m     """
